The system should manage the delivery of static information. Static information is information that does not change once it has been registered with the system.

Two Actors are present, a User and a Site.

Value <Static Information> comprises <name> and <data>.

Use cases for the Site:
  Register Static Information: <Static Information> 
    Insert <Static Information> into the Static Information Repository
    if <Static Information>.<name> has already been registered, whine.

Use cases for the User:
  View Static Information: <name>
    Respond with the <Static Information> having <name>
    if <name> has not been registered, whine.

Classes StaticInformation
